{"tid":311072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"少年長年自慰射牆壁 竟生出大量蟑螂","createTime":"2017-07-06T10:11:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-06T10:17:00.000Z","uid":75737,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6195943eaacfb5fbdb490791fe6e7a6a67c547dd","tid":311072,"uid":75737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T10:11:57.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國有位少年在家沒事就會自慰，弄完就會射在床上或是牆上，而且都是固定的位置，有天他發現自己固定射精的位置出現很多蟑螂，原本他覺得很噁，<span style=\"color: red;\">但想了想發現蟑螂是吃他精液長大的，於是就把蟑螂當小孩一樣照顧</span>，還會讓牠們爬到身上，整件事情被爸媽發現後才停止。<br />\n<br />\n這名少年日前投稿《Reddit》分享他和蟑螂孩子們的故事，雖然已經過了幾個月，但他還是很難過。少年透露，他原本一週會打手槍一次，但近幾年心情不好，幾乎天天打手槍，並會對著床邊或是牆上射精，這種狀況持續了很久，有天他發現房間裡出現了大量的蟑螂，集中在牆上、床邊幾個他固定射精的位置。<br />\n<br />\n少年說，一開始覺得很噁心，不過後來認為，<span style=\"color: red;\">這些蟑螂是在他的精子中出生的</span>，在某個程度上，<span style=\"color: red;\">牠們是自已的後代，於是他開始把蟑螂當作小孩一樣，照顧他們，還會給他們吃食，並讓牠們在自己身上亂爬。</span><br />\n<br />\n不過後來少年的爸爸發現了家裡出現許多蟑螂，立刻打給除蟲公司，除掉蟑螂，<span style=\"color: red;\">他對此很傷心</span>，但是又不能告訴爸媽真相，只好向網友們訴苦。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2122736?utm_medium=P\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2122736%3Futm_medium%3DP&d=3NzjFrGZfXEbbcbOPorIbE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=0b11e12f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2122736%3Futm_medium%3DP&h=11ab07ee\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2122736?utm_medium=P</a>"},{"pid":"1ce070eb3049ea0a8a5ca5133da696f6d0e5405a","tid":311072,"uid":14799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T10:14:03.000Z","msg":"諗返起生蘑菇"},{"pid":"3dfa029ac411b040487b5b9e40b12205e4f46977","tid":311072,"uid":17368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T10:14:04.000Z","msg":"Antman都係咁"},{"pid":"936587ee72cfa76df391e7f9a953c8e78e91972c","tid":311072,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T10:16:49.000Z","msg":"cockman"},{"pid":"9fa80c83c3eda762576142a28db421257de9169b","tid":311072,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T10:16:58.000Z","msg":"Reddit膠post台灣「傳媒」當新聞咁報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44eab00d13920a4fe3e186d580738b78eee8a62f","tid":311072,"uid":54929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T10:17:00.000Z","msg":"痴q線<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}